column2: Recursively assigning properties on objects may cause accidental modification of a built-in prototype object.
column4:
The property chain [["here"|"relative:///index.js:38:16:38:22"]] is recursively assigned to [["target"|"relative:///index.js:59:5:59:10"]] without guarding against prototype pollution.
